description: The floor planks of this long, wide porch creak and groan underfoot, and swinging doors leading inside squeak on their hinges.  Overhead, a wooden awning provides protection from rain.  Square, wooden pillars, part of the rail surrounding the porch, support the awning above.  Several chairs, a bench, and a suspended wooden swing are placed about the porch for watching the road.

The floor planks of this long, wide porch creak and groan underfoot, and swinging doors leading inside squeak on their hinges.  Overhead, a wooden awning provides protection from both sun and rain.  Square, wooden pillars, part of the rail surrounding the porch, support the awning above.  Several chairs, a bench, and a suspended wooden swing are placed about the porch for watching the road.
title: [Trading Post, Front Porch]
